reviewText: Must have for any Darren Hayes' fan.  Great song selection.  Could not ask for more!
Simple Perfect, that's what it is! I'm so happy to buy this item for my collection. Darren Hayes is such a perfect singer. I Loved it!

this is a must have item from singer/songwriter and former frontman of Savage Garden, Darren Hayes. beautifully filmed at the Sydney Opera House in July 2006. i was unable to attend this tour and this is the next best thing. :) if you're able to find it, and u enjoy Darren Hayes or jsut good music in general, GET THIS DVD! im almost afraid to watch it now because the man himself signed it for me.
definately a MUST HAVE item!
